sequenceDiagram
    participant Agent
    participant API
    participant Validator
    participant Normalizer
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Queue as Job Queue
    participant Pipeline as Security Pipeline
    participant WS as WebSocket

    Agent->>API: POST /agent/events (batch)
    API->>Validator: validate each event
    Validator-->>API: ok / errors

    loop Each valid event
        API->>Normalizer: build_normalized_event()
        Normalizer-->>API: normalized_event JSON
        API->>DB: INSERT event
    end

    API->>Queue: enqueue correlation_pipeline
    API->>DB: link offenses + broadcast
    API-->>Agent: 200 {ingested, errors}

    Queue->>Pipeline: run_post_ingestion_pipeline
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: detection
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: correlation
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: timelines
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: threat scoring
    Pipeline->>DB: commit results
    Pipeline->>WS: new_alert broadcasts
